rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0001
rows.name:
Fire Dragons were leading band of
world-class gourmet chefs! On whole
different level to common cook!

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0002
rows.name:
But now they lying in crumpled heap...
What Punin do about food now?

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0003
rows.name:
There nothing else for it...
Must present what food we
have to Emperor and Queen!

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0004
rows.name:
But wait... This could be big
chance to demonstrate culinary
skills of Punin...

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0005
rows.name:
Leave this to Punin!
You head now to Hangar!
